  scheduled from March 2027 to February 2028 at Norfolk Naval Operating Base (NOB), followed by Defueling, scheduled from March 2028 to
  December 2031 at Huntington Ingalls Industries (HII) at Newport News, VA. Dismantlement and Disposal (D&D) is scheduled to begin in
  2031. The completion of an Environmental Assessment (EA) and a government cost estimate are required for the D&D effort. Once completed,
  the ex-CVN 65 D&D and EA will help guide the Navy’s decision on disposal efforts.
