     Surface Warfare Officer's School's Command provides approximately 78,360 officers and enlisted training opportunities annually at 22 learning sites globally.


    This Sub-Activity Group provides support for Career Training Continuum (CTC). In FY 2027, CTC will make progress towards program milestones across all
    three Lines of Effort (LOE) (1-Career-Long Learning Continuums (CLLC), 2-Modern Delivery at Point of Need, and 3-Integrated Content Development).


