II. Force Structure Summary:

Navy off-duty voluntary education programs support the academic needs of over 337,000 active-duty personnel through a single Navy College Virtual Education Center. VOLED
supports more than 300 Navy installations and ships worldwide with face-to-face, mobile, and on-line support features.




