         ensuring continued alignment with Navy priorities for modernization, readiness, and secure enterprise network operations.
         (Baseline: $549)
      xiv)Sexual Assault and Prevention (SAPR): Resources increased for civilian personnel to fund one (1) position that will               190
         implement the Independent Review Commission's (IRC) recommendations to reduce sexual assault in the military as
         mandated by the Secretary of War. (Baseline: $7,785; +1 civilian FTE)


